snippet.textDisplay: Okay this looks badass. It looks like a REAL comic book. I can’t wait , and I feel like DC is going to be blowing Marvel out of the water from now on. Marvel movies always feel like they have something missing. To quote Geralt of Rivia “like a pie without the filling”. GOTG 1+2, Thor: Ragnarok, & Infinity War are all really good, but the rest are “meh”. They don’t feel like a comic book (Ragnarok & GOTG 1+2 so though). Birds of Prey & Wonder Woman 2 trailers are PHENOMENAL, and they have that comic book aesthetic!! With Aquaman, Shazam, Joker, James Gunn to direct the next Suicide Squad & The Robert Pattinson Batman... I think DC is about to dominate. Let’s hope they replace Ava Duvernay as the New Gods director. PLEASE replace Ava Duvernay for the new gods movie!! Marvel is already making the Eternals “woke”, we don’t need New Gods ruined too!!!
